text: Rinchnach is a municipality in the Lower Bavarian district of Regen, of Germany. Rinchnach may also refer to: *Rinchnach (Rinchnacher Ohe), a river of Bavaria, Germany, right tributary of the Rinchnacher Ohe *Rinchnach Priory (Kloster Rinchnach), a former Benedictine house at Rinchnach in Bavaria, Germany
title: Rinchnach (disambiguation)
